text: Taylor is basically an inspiration for me. She has dealt with so much toxicity in her life. Like... way too much. I've been through this too. And I know and understand why she got so much hate. Because she is simply perfect. A perfect person blessed with EVERYTHING. She is so incredibly smart, so tall, her facial features are LITERAL perfection, she's powerful but also kind, she is unbelievably successful and every insecure person would be jeaous of her. These are the reasons she got so much hate and people always tried to bring her down. Because she is much more blessed with beauty, talent, confidence and brains. If you ever think about and wonder why are people always mean to you, just look at yourself a little bit and wonder what you've got that makes other people treat you this way. Look how gorgerous you are, it drives people CRAZY. And never EVER take their words seriously. Because I did. I took their words seriously, I thought about them, I believed what they said about me. And this can lead to insecurity and self-doubt. You know something, we would've all been super confident if nobody never told anything about us or made fun of the way we do somethng.
